title: #92Noon!  9am Hour 8/18 - Jeremiah Sirles, Alex Boone
description: PA & Nordo are back at TCO for the 2nd day of Vikings/49ers.  Former Vikings OL Jeremiah Sirles & Alex Boone stop by the radio perch to talk about their careers, life after football, Justin Jefferson, & more!
